&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;Github&lt;/code&gt; offers the wonderful &lt;a href=&quot;https://pages.github.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;Github Pages&lt;/a
    
    </summary>
    
    
